R2 Object Storage: Starts at $0 with no egress fees Learn how much you could save on monthly egress fees by making the switch Store all of your data with Cloudflare R2 And say goodbye to budget-draining egress fees! Try Cloudflare R2 Today Cloudflare R2 is an S3-compatible object storage that allows you to store large amounts of unstructured data without the costly egress bandwidth fees associated with typical cloud storage services. What sets R2 apart from other object storage providers? If you're a developer, than you know traditional object storage charges for three things: bandwidth, storage size and storage operations. With R2, you'll never pay for bandwidth egress — no matter your request rate. This is great news for developers because egress bandwidth is often the largest charge associated with object storage and is also the hardest charge to predict. Eliminating this is a huge win for open-access to data stored in the cloud. Check out these resources to learn more about Cloudflare R2 Cloudflare Developers Discord - Community tips, insights and best practices R2 Pricing Calculator - Easily calculate how much you'll save when switching R2 Developer Docs - Examples on how to get started and configure R2 R2 Pricing Storage Class A operations Class B operations Forever Free 10 GB / month 1,000,000 / month 10,000,000 / month Monthly Rates $0.015 / GB storage $4.50 / million $0.36 / million R2 starts at $0 and includes free monthly usage. Billing is usage-based after the free threshold is met. Not sure if R2 is right for you? Try it for free and turn it off at any time – usage stops immediately. Try Cloudflare R2 Today Upgrade Plan Login Visit Community Copyright © 2023 Cloudflare, Inc. 101 Townsend Street, San Francisco, CA 94107 Unsubscribe